=Below are the partial audit results from 5 specialized agents.
Inject each section as-is into the correct place in the master report.
Then synthesize all findings to write --Overview--, --recommanded_fixes--, and --final_assessment--.
Deduplicate any overlapping issues across sections. Re-rank --recommanded_fixes-- from CRITICAL → HIGH → MEDIUM → LOW.

Important: each agent's output may include product URLs alongside their findings. Preserve and carry those URLs into the relevant sections and into --recommanded_fixes-- so that every actionable issue is traceable back to its exact product page.

--compatibility_check--
{{ $('Compatibility_check').item.json.output }}

--titles_audit & product_names_audit--
{{ $('Titles & Product Names Verifier').item.json.output }}

--photos_audit--
{{ $('Photos & Visuals Verifier').item.json.output }}

--descriptions_audit--
{{ $('Descriptions & Text Content Verifier').item.json.output }}

--categories_audit--
{{ $json.output }}

Produce the full 9-section master report. No tables. No extra text. No preamble. Start directly with --Overview--.

